    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5276408/" class="title-link">扬之水的书，绝对值得一读。</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5276408"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/MengFan-chih/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u36466095-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/MengFan-chih/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Meng Fan-chih</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-01-20"
      class="main-meta">2012-01-20 21:41:41</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5276408_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  扬之水的书，绝对值得一读。但对于我辈读书人，她的每本书，价格都不菲。初读她的书，是《诗经名物新证》，那还是北京古籍出版社2000年2月的旧版。翻检之下，颇觉新颖别致，而细绎之下，则不得不心下折服，当下诗经学研究的新趋向，实则自这部书始。……

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5276408/#comments">(1回应)</a>
